\begin_layout Standard
Demands for individual level of granularity of information is also strong
 motivation for us.
 As natural, people want to listen to their own stories and there are many
 examples.
 1) many of young people have their personal facebook, blog or webpage where
 they put their personal stories.
 One sometimes writes her diary and shopping list, puts her photos, and
 share those stories with friends and family.
 2) personal health monitoring application is also a good example of such
 demands.
 Recently, Nike+iPod package provides individual with their traning/running
 story on a daily basis which is of great success.
 Some elderly people, who have potential heal problems, are willing to buy
 personal blood pressure monitor/blood sugar level monitor.
 3) Curiousity often makes us want to know how well we are doing.
 Typical video game gives us some numbers that indicate how good a player
 is.
 Grade and competition often motivate students to study harder.
