\begin_layout Standard
Technically speaking, sensing of people and sensing of phenomena are nothing
 new.
 However, sensing of how well and how are people doing with the world in
 individual level is a new question that is very interesting to answer.
 This is unanswered and our work tries to answer to this question.
 First of all, we try to find some interaction models between a user and
 an environment, i.e.
 an appliance.
 Some of prior arts that are related to 
